additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: INGREDIENTS: Dairy ingredients (reconstituted skim milk and/or reconstituted buttermilk, butter oil, cream), sugar, cocoa components (12%^)(cocoa mass, cocoa butter), glucose, vegetable oil, emulsifiers (E471, soy lecithin, sunflower lecithin), stabilisers (E412, E410, E407, E401), natural vanilla, flavour, colour (E160b), pea protein, salt, maltodextrin, erythritol, sucralose. Contains milk and soy. May contain gluten containing cereals (wheat, barley), peanuts and tree nuts.

additionalProperty.name: Allergen
additionalProperty.value: May Be Present Barley, May Be Present Tree Nuts, May Be Present Peanuts, May Be Present Wheat, Contains Soy, Contains Milk
